<P>
Column; Restaurant Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062190-0031 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 236393 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 21, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
