LIBERATION ORGANIZATION; TERRORISM -- ISRAEL; ABBAS, ABUL; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN POLICY; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- 
ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO 
</P>
