<P>
CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; SECRECY; MEETINGS; PROPOSITION 112 (STATE 
ETHICS COMMISSION); LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; PUBLIC ACCESS 
