Streetbeat High-Steppers, Avalon Park, 700 E. Gardena Blvd., 538-0019; ages 6 
to 13. Carson Queenettes for children 3 to 21, Mills Park, 1340 Dimondale 
Drive; 631-3130. 
</P>
