$72 a week. Summer Day Camp for first- to sixth-graders from June 25 to Sept. 7 
from 7 a.m. to 6 p.m.; $90 a week. Family Camp on Labor Day weekend. Swimming 
lessons for ages 6 months to 14 years, starting June 25. One-week camp program 
from July 14 to July 21 at Camp Round Meadow in San Bernardino for fourth- to 
sixth-graders; $190; 327-0750. 
