cartoon drawing on Sunday mornings for ages 8 to 13 and Tuesday afternoon for 
older children. The department offers basic reading, writing and arithmetic 
classes; dance, gymnastics, baton twirling, tennis, karate, ice-skating and 
chess; 217-9537. 
