Summer Reading Program -- Movies, crafts, clowns and magic -- and books -- will 
be available for children in kindergarten through sixth grade at the Hermosa 
Beach Library, 550 Pier Ave.; Wednesdays at 2 p.m., June 27 through Aug. 22. 
Sponsored by Hermosa Beach Friends of the Library; 379-8475. 
</P>
