four or five weeks and begin June 25 and July 2. Hours are from 9 a.m. to 3 
p.m. or 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. Child care is available before and after camp. For 
five-week sessions, cost is $72 for Inglewood residents and $86 for 
non-residents. For four-week sessions, cost is $58 for residents and $70 for 
