Los Angeles County 
</P>
<P>
Jr. Athletic Workshop Day Camp -- Nine weeks of basic instruction in tennis, 
swimming, racquetball and other sports for ages 6 to 12. Also field trips, 
crafts and talent shows, sponsored by the South End Racquet and Health Club in 
Torrance, 2800 Sky Park Drive. Activities from 9 a.m. to 3 p.m. daily, with 
before-care beginning at 8 a.m. and after-care until 6 p.m. Lunch included. 
June 25 through Aug. 26. Price to non-members is $135 for the first week, $115 
for all subsequent weeks, plus $2 an hour for before- and after-care. Discounts 
for siblings and club members; 530-0630. 
