<TEXT>
<P>
Water quality issues facing San Gabriel Valley business and property owners 
will be the focus of a meeting on Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
Members of the South El Monte Property Owners Assn. have been upset by the way 
regulatory agencies have handled water contamination problems. The group will 
host the talks, in which regional water quality officials will discuss how 
pollution laws affect small businesses. 
</P>
