<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Service Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Poll Shows Support for Green Energy: The Coalition for Energy Efficiency and 
Renewable Technologies (CEERT) said a public opinion poll showed strong support 
in California for renewable and efficient energy sources. Almost nine out of 10 
Californians believe that state government should encourage environmentally 
sound energy use, according to CEERT, and 70% said they would be willing to pay 
more to get it. CEERT is a California-based coalition of environmentalist 
groups and renewable energy companies. 
</P>
</TEXT>
