</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
COALITION FOR ENERGY EFFICIENCY AND RENEWABLE TECHNOLOGIES; ENVIRONMENT; ENERGY 
-- CALIFORNIA; ALTERNATIVE ENERGY; PUBLIC OPINION; CONSERVATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062190-0164 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 236793 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 21, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
