</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Two Baby Bells in Second Czech Venture: US West and Bell Atlantic signed a 
letter of intent with Czechoslovakian authorities to form a joint venture 
company to build a public switched-packet data network in the Eastern European 
nation. On June 15, the same parties agreed to construct a national cellular 
system and work together to modernize the telecommunications infrastructure in 
Czechoslovakia. 
</P>
