Bruin weight events Coach Art Venegas is impressed with Millet's composure 
under pressure. ; Photo, UCLA junior Tracie Millet became the only Bruin track 
and field performer to win two NCAA individual championships at one meet. She 
was first in the discus and shot put. 
</P>
