including three before-school sessions at 6 p.m. at USC. ; Photo, When she was 
12, Booker swam the fifth-fastest backstroke and the 18th-fastest freestyle 
times ever in that age group. ; Photo, Booker, who with weighted honors courses 
has a 4.2 grade-point average, wants to go to medical school. LISA ROMEREIN / 
Los Angeles Times 
