FOOTNOTES; 
</P>
<P>
DUTCH CLUB DEALING FOR RAMOS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MILAN, Italy 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JC Roda of the Netherlands' first division has offered U.S. midfielder Tab 
Ramos a three-year contract. The U.S. Soccer Federation is asking for a 
$750,000 transfer fee, a figure the club has balked at. 
</P>
<P>
Ramos would prefer a two-year or one-year deal, but nothing can happen until 
the transfer fee is worked out. 
</P>
</TEXT>
